{"tid":1294770,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"《Uncharted》電影導演確認將不會直接採用遊戲劇情","createTime":"2019-07-08T00:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:45:19.000Z","uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"73982fe1f1a49da66f2e672a1bebefba4c2f3d05","tid":1294770,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:06:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2374111356192705\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNowzPlay%2Fposts%2F2374111356192705&d=Tc8prIKBo9hF1z3tnQ%2BJRpB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=e9a35c32\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NowzPlay/posts/2374111356192705</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RK6rxYc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRK6rxYc.jpg&h=f1ce782f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>【業界】《Uncharted》電影導演確認將不會直接採用遊戲劇情</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  《Uncharted》電影目前已經定檔2020年12月18日上映，不過關於該片的具體細節始終嚴格保密。比如大家最關心的一個問題就是，電影中Nathan Drake究竟會踏上怎樣的冒險。因為演員Tom Holland扮演的是年輕時期的Drake，所以劇情方面可能有很大發揮空間。<br />\n<br />\n  最近，在接受媒體採訪時，該片導演Dan Trachtenberg透露了一些消息，看起來，《Uncharted》電影的劇情將不會套用遊戲劇情，因為那樣的遊戲改編電影只能提供二流體驗。<br />\n<br />\n  在採訪中，Trachtenberg特別提到了他想要避免走上老路。<strong><ins> &ldquo;我曾經收到過這個故事的不同版本，但沒有任何版本讓我感到有趣，因為我並不想走遊戲已經走過的路。&rdquo;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  他繼續講解道，複製與粘貼出來的作品永遠都不可能超越遊戲原本的體驗。 <strong><ins>&ldquo;我覺得在拍攝遊戲改編電影的時候，照搬遊戲劇情是毫無價值的。如果我們單純地複制遊戲內容，那麼只能提供二流體驗，不可能超過他們在遊戲中已經獲得過的難忘體驗。&rdquo;</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  Trachtenberg對他和創意團隊目前編寫出來的劇情表現出很強的自信。 &ldquo;如果Naughty Dog想要再以Drake和Sullivan為主角再次製作一部《Uncharted》的話，那麼電影的劇情很可能會提供很好的參考和借鑒。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  目前《Uncharted》電影尚未公佈劇照、海報或宣傳片，<strong><ins>事實上，本片的選角甚至可能還沒有完成。直到今年3月份，Sony依然在尋找Sullivan的合適扮演者。</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n  如果一切進展順利，《Uncharted》電影將於2020年12月18日上映。<br />\n<br />\n-----"},{"pid":"030d36a449f7ad4fed32a5846d4db9421caeddf0","tid":1294770,"uid":3405,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:09:09.000Z","msg":"遺跡破壞者"},{"pid":"476eaa88a1cb61b8f8a7a4577ee53ca596aeb955","tid":1294770,"uid":111253,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:11:35.000Z","msg":"搵個劇透撚做主角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b75f096e500b58ef42bd55ec0e89d78f497d6e","tid":1294770,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T00:58:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"832d04d087542a2f56ae8bcbe528e77d23de517b","tid":1294770,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"隻game之前網上特價1-4集好似都係一舊水左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8184a1c6e81dc611dce20e4345671d2ff3fba6a","tid":1294770,"uid":121286,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:28:49.000Z","msg":"隻game每集死好多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820a2749972b718110dc805777b2b8c83ed8db9f","tid":1294770,"uid":172677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832d04d087542a2f56ae8bcbe528e77d23de517b","tid":1294770,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T01:01:27.000Z","msg":"隻game之前網上特價1-4集好似都係一舊水左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T06:45:19.000Z","msg":"抵<br />\n好撚好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}